    DimsNCHW will be removed in a future version of TensorRT, use Dims instead.

    IOutputDimensionsFormula has been superseded by PaddingMode.
    org.bytedeco.tensorrt.nvinfer.IPluginLayer
    This interface is superseded by IPluginV2Layer \warning Do not inherit from this class, as doing so will break forward-compatibility of the API and ABI.

    This interface is superseded by IRNNv2Layer. \warning Do not inherit from this class, as doing so will break forward-compatibility of the API and ABI.
